In fact, I find their treatment of workers, especially in fulfillment centers, disgraceful on both a <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2018/nov/28/new-york-labor-leaders-amazon-workers">social</a> and <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/aug/18/amazon-regime-making-british-staff-physically-and-mentally-ill-says-union">personal</a> level.</p>

